ughout a grid, conductivity issues along the way often lead to energy loss. There are numerous systems in testing and development, such as ultra-high voltage transmission (UHV), which can transmit electricity significantly more rapidly and effectively than comparable systems, and it\u2019s being ", mdx("a", _extends({
